name: Envision-default-model
tagline: Default and Role Model Changes to current version of Envision. Testing with three groups of engineers.
body:
### Envision Default and Role Model study.
This research project is measuring the effects of adding default and role models projects to engineering decision making when using a rating system for sustainability. 

### Code
Here you will find the code for the modified rating system software. 

### Contact
If you have questions or would like to collaborate on the project please contact me at tshealy (at) vt (dot) edu
